    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This driver-focused machine features a high-revving naturally aspirated powerplant paired with a precise close-ratio 6-speed manual transmission. The valvetrain is exceptionally quiet, and the linear power delivery is complemented by a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from a recently refreshed suspension setup with upgraded bushings for improved turn-in and lateral stability. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanicals are stout\u2014boasting excellent compression and crisp gear synchronization. Equipped with four-piston monoblock calipers and ventilated rotors, the braking performance is fade-resistant and communicative. A mechanically sound example ready for spirited canyon runs or daily engagement.",
