      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior boasts a deep, lustrous finish with only minor, expected signs of careful road use, while the alloy wheels remain crisp and clean. Inside, the cabin welcomes you with premium leather upholstery that has been regularly conditioned; the seats remain supportive and the dash is free of sun damage or cracks. Every electronic feature\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, having undergone regular fluid changes and preventative maintenance, ensuring a smooth, quiet ride and confident handling. It comes with a complete set of service records and two sets of keys, representing a reliable opportunity for a discerning buyer seeking a high-quality daily driver that has been treated with genuine care.",
